        },
        "text": "At the same time, we stress the importance of ensuring that such measures do not undermine fundamental rights, particularly the right to privacy and the freedom to use end-to-end encrypted communications. The regulation must not lead to disproportionate surveillance or mandatory data accessibility for authorities.",
